Product Description

Dramatic from every angle, the Bijou Collection presents as a glamorous statement to the décor of your boudoir. The unique profile of the Eastern King bed features a V-notch design that serves as not only as a focal point, but as inspiration for the woven pattern that fronts each piece of the collection. The back-lit faux leather headboard insert is featured in a champagne tone that perfectly complements the champagne finish of the collection. The mirrored framing of the bed provides subtle reflection and distinct accent. The drawers of the storage footboard are fronted with triangle-shaped polished chrome hardware and distinct geometric framing.
